Package model.entity

Class Player

java.lang.Object
model.entity.Player
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Crewmate, Impostor
public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
This class represents a Player. A Player has several attributes to store the current room, last room, the role, the color index, the map and other attributes to manage crewmates and impostors.
Version:
22/5/2021
Author:
Riccardo Giacalone (ricardo.giacalone@students.salle.url.edu), Guillermo Gonzalez (guillermo.g@students.salle.url.edu), Oscar Cubeles (oscar.cubeles@students.salle.url.edu), Goddy Clinton (weriwohmbang.g@students.salle.url.edu)
